<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Job Posted</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1b65b2 0%, #8fb2d6 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .info-box { background: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: #1b65b2; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(27, 101, 178, 0.4); }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ’¼ New Job Posted</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi Admin,</p>
      
      <p>A new job has been posted on the platform and requires review.</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{companyName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
        <p><strong>Posted on:</strong> {{postDate}}</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Please review the job posting to ensure it meets platform guidelines before it goes live.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{jobUrl}}" class="button">Review Job Posting</a>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Review checklist:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Job description is clear and appropriate</li>
        <li>Requirements are reasonable</li>
        <li>Company information is accurate</li>
        <li>Complies with platform policies</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} System</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated notification.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
